<h1 id="section">!!!</h1>
<p>A heading that slugs to nothing falls back to a reserved
identifier.</p>
<h1 id="section-1">???</h1>
<p>Another empty slug is disambiguated against the fallback.</p>
<h1 id="foo">Foo</h1>
<p>A base identifier.</p>
<h1 id="foo-1">Foo</h1>
<p>A repeat gains a numeric suffix.</p>
<h1 id="foo-1-1">Foo 1</h1>
<p>A title that already carries the suffix is disambiguated further.</p>
<h1 id="i-here">İ here</h1>
<p>A dotted capital I lowercases to a letter plus a combining mark that
the identifier drops.</p>
<h1 id="wordend">WordͅEnd</h1>
<p>A letter-like combining mark is not a letter and is dropped from the
identifier.</p>
